OL,3,CCommunity nurse jailed for sexually
OL,4,Cassaulting elderly woman in her home
OL,6,FA community nurse has been jailed for
OL,7,Ffour and a half years for sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting an 85-year-old woman in her
OL,9,Fown home.
OL,11,FSteven Hicks, 60, visited the woman,
OL,12,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,13,Fon 22 December 2021 during a routine
OL,14,Fvisit.
OL,16,FHicks, from Woodley, Reading,
OL,17,Fperformed examinations but he also
OL,18,Fclaimed he moisturised her lower body,
OL,19,Fto account for his DNA being at the
OL,20,Fscene, but this was not recorded on
OL,21,Fhis notes.
