OL,6,FThe victim, who is now 87, had been
OL,7,Freceiving regular visits to her home
OL,8,Fin Earley from nurses and carers
OL,9,Ffollowing a fall on 19 December 2021.
OL,11,FOn 5 January 2022, Hicks arrived
OL,12,Funannounced at the property, a day
OL,13,Fafter the woman's evening visits were
OL,14,Fcancelled as her condition was
OL,15,Fimproving.
OL,17,FThe woman described a man dressed in
OL,18,FPPE, surgical mask, a plastic apron
OL,19,Fand gloves, as well as glasses.
