OL,4,Cassaulting elderly woman in her home
OL,6,FAt Reading Crown Court on Friday 19
OL,7,FJanuary 2024, the jury of eight women
OL,8,Fand four men found Hicks guilty of
OL,9,Fsexual assault after seven hours and
OL,10,F43 minutes of deliberation.
OL,12,FThroughout the almost two-week trial,
OL,13,FHicks claimed he couldn't remember
OL,14,Fwhere he was at the time of the
OL,15,Fassault.
OL,17,FOn the day of the attack, Hicks said
OL,18,Fhe spent time with his son in the
OL,19,Fafternoon, but he could not account
OL,20,Ffor his whereabouts afterwards.
