OL,6,FHe said: "I was asked by an officer to
OL,7,Fput this information to them, I
OL,8,Fhonestly can't remember - year before,
OL,9,Fa specific location, date and time, I
OL,10,Fcan't give it. I can give
OL,11,Fpossibilities."
OL,13,FHowever, not only did mobile phone
OL,14,Fdata place him near the victim's house
OL,15,Fat the time of the incident, but CCTV
OL,16,Fnearby showed a man matching his
OL,17,Fdescription in the area too.
OL,19,FHis DNA matched one found at the scene
OL,20,Fmore than 15 days later.
