OL,6,FSpecialist investigator, Philippa
OL,7,FSharman from Thames Valley Police,
OL,8,Fsaid the main issue in the case was
OL,9,Faround identity as it was unknown who
OL,10,Fthe masked man was. But once the DNA
OL,11,Fevidence came back, they were able to
OL,12,Farrest Hicks.
OL,14,FPhilippa Sharman said: "Having
OL,15,Finterviewed him (Steven Hicks) a
OL,16,Fnumber of times, I don't know how to
OL,17,Fdescribe him.
