OL,6,FShe said: "Personally, for something
OL,7,Fso relevant I would hope you remember
OL,8,Fthe detail we needed. Is it the case
OL,9,Fhe can't give us that details because
OL,10,Fhe was at the complainant's address?"
OL,12,FDuring the sentencing hearing at
OL,13,FReading Crown Court, Judge Kirsty Real
OL,14,Ftold Hicks: "You went to the home of
OL,15,Fan elderly woman in the evening and
OL,16,Fyou had no legitimate reason to go
OL,17,Fthere. It was a deception.
