OL,9,Fcarers would not be there. There is a
OL,10,Fvery high degree of abuse of trust
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"You affected your victim's sense of
OL,14,Findependence and safety in her own
OL,15,Fhome - and you have undermined her
OL,16,Ftrust in other carers."
