OL,6,FThe victim's impact statement which
OL,7,Fwas read out at Reading Crown Court
OL,8,Fsaid: "One of the worst parts of
OL,9,Fthinking about what happened to me is
OL,10,Fthe worry that it could happen to my
OL,11,Fgranddaughters as easily as it
OL,12,Fhappened to me.
OL,14,F"What happened to me should have never
OL,15,Fhappened. I am 87 years old now and I
OL,16,Fshould be able to trust the services
OL,17,Fput in place to help me recover at
OL,18,Fhome."
